title: Elgato EyeTV 3.6.5 build (7310) Latest + SN 155 MB
description:
Elgato EyeTV 3.6.5 build (7310) Latest + SN 155 MB



Highlights

*Watch, pause, and rewind live TV on your Mac
*Search the Program Guide using multiple criteria
*Record one show or an entire TV series
*Edit out unwanted content and create clips from your recordings
*Export recordings to iTunes automatically for playback on an iPhone or iPad
*Share recordings with other Macs on your local network
*Stream live or recorded TV to an iPhone or iPad with the optional EyeTV app

System Requirements

EyeTV 3.6 and all future EyeTV updates are only available for Mac computers with an Intel processor. PowerPC processors are no longer supported. EyeTV 3.6 will work on an Intel Mac with OS X 10.5.8 or higher. Recommend OS X 10.8.2 or later with all software and security updates installed

Use Little Snitch to block eyetv from calling home
